1
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,720
The maids who served Queen Yun

2
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,720
have almost all disappeared.

3
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:15,650
Only Huixin remains in the palace.

4
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:17,040
Moreover,

5
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,960
given Consort Yu's temperament,

6
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,560
how could she keep such a huge risk

7
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,640
by her side?

8
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,480
So I think

9
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,840
there must be a reason why Huixin

10
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:29,320
would never betray Consort Yu even to the death.

11
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:29,850
Alright.

12
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:32,010
I will ask Zeng Le

13
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,620
to thoroughly investigate this Huixin.

14
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:38,930
How about

15
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,920
we get a physician to look at you?

16
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,840
No need.

17
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:45,840
Rest assured,

18
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,400
I am fine.

19
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,520
I will absolutely not let this kind of thing

20
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,920
happen a second time.

21
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,520
Anli pays her respects to you, Aunt.

22
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,530
You are quite well-behaved today.

23
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,040
I heard

24
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,320
you went to see Hao yesterday.

25
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,160
I just felt

26
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,720
that I should get closer to the Second Prince

27
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:36,579
so as not to let down your painstaking cultivation.

28
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:39,800
It seems you have figured it out.

29
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,240
It wasn't in vain for me to spend

30
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,680
so much effort on you.

31
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:51,520
Today,

32
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,760
why don't I see Aunt Huixin?

33
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,680
Let me help you with your makeup, Aunt.

34
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:30,040
Aunt Huixin.

35
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,090
Ling Xueyue,

36
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,780
you actually betrayed Her Highness.

37
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,040
Loyalty comes first,

38
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,280
then betrayal.

39
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,760
I, Ling Xueyue,

40
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,080
have only ever trusted myself.

41
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,320
How is that betrayal?

42
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,690
Don't forget

43
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,400
you still have poison in you.

44
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,659
Do you not want to live?

45
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:07,570
Since the day I entered the palace,

46
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,560
I have put my life on the line.

47
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:11,680
Consort Yu poisoned me

48
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,880
just to control me

49
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:16,000
and make me obey her.

50
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:17,840
In the end,

51
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,680
I am just a puppet.

52
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,800
When it's done,

53
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:25,200
I'm afraid my life will also be over.

54
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,200
You think quite clearly.

55
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,640
However,

56
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,800
even if you defect to the First Prince,

57
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,000
it's still a dead end.

58
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:34,600
The poison in you,

59
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,940
besides Her Highness,

60
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:37,960
no one can cure it.

61
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,480
No one can cure it?

62
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,200
The drug in your body,

63
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,480
once taken,

64
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:46,140
can never be cured.

65
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:48,920
You can only rely on medicine to stay alive.

66
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:51,120
Only by constantly taking the antidote

67
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,580
will the poison not act up.

68
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:53,490
Originally,

69
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,880
you could have had a chance of survival.

70
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:58,880
Could it be

71
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:02,810
that this is the reason you are loyal to Her Highness?

72
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:06,920
Aunt Huixin,

73
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,520
regardless of the truth

74
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:12,090
about the night Queen Yun passed away,

75
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:15,840
since you secretly went to pay respects to her,

76
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:16,840
it means

77
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:17,960
you

78
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,770
are not a malicious person.

79
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,570
Miss, you don't need to waste your breath.

80
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:23,480
I...

81
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,040
I know nothing.

82
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,600
I don't expect you to tell the truth

83
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,520
right now.

84
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,360
I'm just curious.

85
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:36,600
Is Her Highness

86
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,920
really worthy of your loyalty?

87
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,320
You stayed in Yuze Palace all night,

88
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:45,280
yet you return unharmed.

89
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,640
If Her Highness finds out,

90
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,610
what will she think?

91
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,960
If Her Highness knew I betrayed her,

92
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,280
would she be suspicious?

93
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:04,050
You've been in contact with me for so long,

94
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:06,240
and you haven't noticed at all?

95
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,420
I've served Her Highness for so long.

96
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,720
How could a few words from you

97
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,780
make me betray her?

98
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,380
Your Highness,

99
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,480
if there is nothing else,

100
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,740
I'll take my leave.

101
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:34,680
Tingfeng,

102
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:37,400
escort Aunt Huixin back to her palace.

103
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:39,770
Yes, Your Highness.

104
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,770
Aunt Huixin,

105
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,010
this way please.

106
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,840
You came back from Yuze Palace.

107
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:03,050
Forgive me, Your Highness.

108
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,720
Last night, for some reason,

109
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,000
I was knocked unconscious by Guard Gu

110
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,320
and taken to Yuze Palace for questioning.

111
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,280
His Highness

112
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,720
asked about the past of Queen Yun.

113
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,200
Queen Yun?

114
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,960
I don't know why

115
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,800
His Highness asked about it,

116
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,220
but I didn't say a word.

117
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,320
I see you

118
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:22,000
slept quite well yesterday.

119
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,280
I heard

120
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,850
early this morning,

121
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:27,480
Gu Tingfeng escorted you back himself.

122
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,920
I swear I said nothing.

123
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,420
It was Ling Xueyue.

124
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,409
That girl betrayed us long ago.

125
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:35,320
You've been in contact with Ling Xueyue for so long,

126
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,280
and you didn't notice anything?

127
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,480
You come to me early in the morning to tell me

128
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,740
that girl betrayed me.

129
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,840
Do you think I'm a fool?

130
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,159
Your Highness,

131
00:08:44,159 --> 00:08:45,600
I really know nothing.

132
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,460
Come to think of it,

133
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,380
Ling Xueyue

134
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,960
might have had ulterior motives from the start.

135
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,760
His Highness chose so many maids,

136
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:54,040
but he picked her.

137
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,300
Perhaps

138
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,410
she knew His Highness already.

139
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,960
She worked obediently for you,

140
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,480
probably to

141
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:04,180
investigate the truth of Queen Yun's death.

142
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:07,080
Why should I believe you?

143
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,380
Your Highness,

144
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,140
last night,

145
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,320
I was taken to Yuze Palace.

146
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,760
They only asked a few questions

147
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,400
and sent me back.

148
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,440
It means His Highness has no evidence

149
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:18,960
to prove

150
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,520
that Queen Yun's death wasn't an accident.

151
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:23,000
He just wanted to test you.

152
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:24,610
You mustn't fall for it.

153
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:28,160
Your Highness,

154
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:30,280
my family has been under your care for years.

155
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,880
We have no ulterior motives.

156
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,560
My life is yours.

157
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,000
I would never betray you.

158
00:09:35,880 --> 00:09:38,200
You know the consequences of betraying me.

159
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:38,880
I know.

160
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:39,960
I know.

161
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,240
Your Highness,

162
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,300
please believe me.

163
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,360
How can I trust you again?

164
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,920
If the crime of murdering the prince

165
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:50,720
and the late queen is confirmed,

166
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,920
let alone me,

167
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:55,360
the entire Baishi clan will be implicated.

168
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,020
Your Highness.

169
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,120
Your Highness,

170
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,720
please trust me one more time.

171
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,520
The servants who served the late queen

172
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,040
have long vanished without a trace.

173
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,680
No matter how the First Prince investigates,

174
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,740
he won't be able to find any evidence.

175
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,130
As for the First Prince,

176
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:10,090
as long as Ling Xueyue disappears,

177
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,170
then this matter

178
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,860
will vanish into thin air.

179
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:14,420
Your Highness.

180
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:15,900
Your Highness.

181
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:18,680
Get up.

182
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,860
Thank you, Your Highness.

183
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:30,840
Pingle,

184
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,890
you can leave the palace tomorrow.

185
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:34,900
Your Highness,

186
00:10:35,160 --> 00:10:37,000
you want to deal with Consort Yu alone?

187
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,730
Don't worry.

188
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:39,120
I'm not letting you go because I suspect

189
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,450
you work for Consort Yu.

190
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,240
Your Highness, do you

191
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:44,040
not have a single doubt about me?

192
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:46,060
If it were anyone else,

193
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,280
I might hesitate.

194
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,560
But not you.

195
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:57,890
What's the difference?

196
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:03,360
Because you are the person I want to trust the most.

197
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:07,480
Xueyue.

198
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:08,740
Your Highness,

199
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,930
Your Highness's trust,

200
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,080
I don't know if I can bear it.

201
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:19,520
Actually,

202
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,760
the medicine you give me every day,

203
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,090
I had Tingfeng check it,

204
00:11:23,400 --> 00:11:24,730
and it's not poisonous.

205
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:28,440
So all this time,

206
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,480
you were just playing along.

207
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,320
You have already deceived Consort Yu once.

208
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:35,180
If she finds out you are disloyal,

209
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,800
in the future,

210
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:39,580
I won't be able to protect you.

211
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:42,640
So,

212
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,640
everything you've done

213
00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:48,160
is to protect me?

214
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:49,760
For you,

215
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:51,890
and also for myself.

216
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,520
Your Highness is up early today.

217
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:02,740
His Majesty hasn't returned from court yet.

218
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,540
I haven't been sleeping well lately.

219
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,840
It's better to stay awake.

220
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,640
Then I'll go to the Imperial Hospital

221
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:12,900
and get a prescription to help you sleep.

222
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:17,160
Among all the maids in the palace,

223
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:18,560
you are the one

224
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,880
who comforts me the most.

225
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:24,320
I have served you for a long time,

226
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,200
so naturally I know your habits

227
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,560
better than others.

228
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:30,920
Huixin.

229
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:34,260
Your brother's birthday is coming up, isn't it?

230
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,130
I've prepared a small gift.

231
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,800
Go and deliver it for me.

232
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:41,320
You haven't seen them in a long time, have you?

233
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,060
Your Highness,

234
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:46,280
tomorrow is the late queen's memorial ceremony.

235
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:48,140
There are still many things to do.

236
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,730
Let me stay and help you.

237
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:52,520
Everything that needs to be prepared is ready.

238
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:55,440
I'll grant you half a day off.

239
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,680
Just be back before sunset.

240
00:12:58,680 --> 00:13:00,840
Th-Thank you, Your Highness.

241
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:03,440
Go on.

242
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:29,650
The people up there,

243
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:30,560
leave no one alive.
